  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882620/extras/7d7d4570e3062947e312c9f9dff4ddad.avif?t=1723135906\" width=600 height=110 /></span><br>This is your next great opportunity to dive into 16-bit classic consoles era and master your play-skill. <strong>Zeon 25</strong> is an amazing 2D Shoot’Em Up experience with 90’s vibes and hardcore gameplay. Click «Start» and try to finish the game!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882620/extras/a990d87dd9819449273399b998312bde.avif?t=1723135906\" width=600 height=110 /></span><br>In this game you play as a brave Corporal Johnson facing many encounters. Game features include:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Story mode with three chapters<br></li><li> More than 50 types of enemies to defeat<br></li><li> Extreme boss battles<br></li><li> Special arcade mode<br></li><li> Ship upgrade-system<br></li><li> Good pixel graphics<br></li><li> Rhythmic soundtrack</li></ul>",
